data.description: This home is one of Leander's Lakeline Ranch Subdivision masterpiece 2 story home.     This house welcomes you with an upstairs loft that includes beautiful wall cut-outs overlooking the spacious dining room and den area. The kitchen opens to the living room that is completed with a cozy fireplace. This house is also located in an area that is zoned for highly ranked schools and close to restaurants, shopping and entertainment.     3 bedrooms/2.5 bathrooms PLUS bonus loft.  Large backyard!
